Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.10,0:01:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動手前想清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.79,0:01:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此 才會反被我利用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.93,0:01:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要中這種非常明顯的陷阱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.46,0:01:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者要沉著冷靜地判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你說 我早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.40,0:01:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是看你不懂才這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.22,0:01:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.67,0:01:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的一舉一動 真是漏洞百出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.00,0:02:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.76,0:02:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於讓我找到破綻了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.03,0:02:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.70,0:02:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 你這個傢伙太過分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是替身術
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.68,0:02:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的手裡劍暴露了我的藏身之處
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.72,0:02:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是故意露出破綻的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死 我怎麼會上當呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.03,0:02:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 你在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道已經被老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.74,0:02:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助絕不會發生那種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.66,0:02:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有被發現
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:02:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻 小心後面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫做「沉著冷靜地判斷」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不會再中老師設下的陷阱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.91,0:03:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼又上當了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不及格 卡卡西的結論
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 剛才怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.38,0:03:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.40,0:03:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:03:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:03:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有點過火了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.89,0:04:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在才察覺 似乎太晚了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.27,0:04:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的聲音…是小櫻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者戰術的心得之二
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻術
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻那傢伙 很簡單就上當了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻術…幻覺催眠術的一種
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.39,0:04:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也難怪那傢伙會輕易上當了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟那些傢伙不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.29,0:04:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是等你搶到鈴鐺之後再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣直接衝過來是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.35,0:05:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是陷阱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小子真不簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.38,0:05:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下可沒空看《親熱天堂》了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 我是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.98,0:06:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助剛才滿身是血
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我親眼看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.95,0:06:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 不要拋下我先去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.46,0:06:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來圓柱後面是那個樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來便當就放在石頭上面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者要沉著冷靜地判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.84,0:06:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我承認 你跟他兩的確不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.69,0:06:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.14,0:06:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火遁.豪火球之術
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 下忍居然會這種忍術
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:07:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的查克拉應該還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.36,0:07:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.57,0:07:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在後面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 上面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土遁.心中斬首術
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者戰術心得之三
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍術
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.59,0:07:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 不能動了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過在我看來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.28,0:07:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很快就能嶄露頭角了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就叫做打壓新秀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:07:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.15,0:08:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便沒有傻乎乎地去搶鈴鐺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.97,0:08:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要躲在這裡把便當吃掉 我也就滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.58,0:08:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他之間居然差這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.60,0:08:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是死人頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.15,0:08:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在搞什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 你平安無事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我 不要這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快到中午了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.94,0:09:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間緊張 我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.88,0:09:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 你還想繼續搶鈴鐺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才已經摸到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定能得手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.29,0:09:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助 你果然是很厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.22,0:09:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師那麼厲害 我絕對搶不到鈴鐺的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.09,0:09:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 我就不能和佐助在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.07,0:09:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正時間也不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.04,0:09:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次就不要逞強了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:10:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界上 只有我才能殺得了那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.11,0:10:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.68,0:10:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說老師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候…我哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.02,0:10:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟在說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一個復仇者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要超越那個傢伙才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.21,0:10:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒空在這裡跟你耗著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要親手宰了那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢話太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.90,0:10:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.83,0:11:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個肚子都餓得呱呱叫了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.02,0:11:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 關於這次的演習
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.45,0:11:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看你們也沒有必要回忍者學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我剛剛只是昏倒而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也能算及格嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.33,0:11:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛情勝利了 真是太帥了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.95,0:11:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.32,0:11:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就表示 我們三個人都…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.88,0:11:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 你們三個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不必再當忍者了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到目前為止 還沒有一個學生及格過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.40,0:11:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊魯卡 我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在讓那些孩子們去當忍者是不是正確
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.29,0:12:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 卡卡西的判斷是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.69,0:12:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不用當忍者了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.61,0:12:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.31,0:12:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的確沒有搶到鈴鐺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可也沒必要讓我們放棄做忍者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.55,0:12:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.77,0:12:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個都是沒有資格做忍者的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會說你是小鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.17,0:12:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把你的腳踩在佐助的頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你們幾個 是不是瞧不起忍者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.13,0:12:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們認為為什麼要分組進行這個演習呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.68,0:12:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思就是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個完全沒有搞懂這個測驗的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:12:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.60,0:13:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判斷你們是否能通過這個測驗的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以從剛才起 我就想問這個問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們腦袋裡裝的是不是漿糊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們懂不懂三人一組的用意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.74,0:13:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人一組又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是團隊合作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們互相幫助嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是 不過現在才知道已經晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們三個一起上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.43,0:13:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定可以搶到鈴鐺哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.06,0:13:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還真是可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.06,0:13:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.68,0:13:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是鈴鐺只有兩個 要怎麼團隊合作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人拚命搶鈴鐺的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.96,0:13:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一個人一定要忍耐了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.79,0:13:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣怎麼團隊合作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會起內訌的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.38,0:13:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們故意安排成會起內訌的測驗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個考試的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:14:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要選拔出在這種情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.35,0:14:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能不顧自己的利益
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.56,0:14:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優先執行團隊合作的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是看看你們自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.56,0:14:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.42,0:14:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不把鳴人放在眼裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.59,0:14:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿腦子只有不知身在何處的佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.14,0:14:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老是一個人橫衝直撞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.85,0:14:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你則把他們兩個當成了絆腳石
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去單打獨鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.78,0:14:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務是以小組來執行的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.91,0:14:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對忍者來說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.07,0:14:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卓越的個人技術的確不可或缺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 團隊合作卻比這個更為重要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂團隊合作的獨行俠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會讓同伴陷入危機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至還會送命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.95,0:14:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舉個例子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.31,0:14:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻 把鳴人殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然佐助就死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.07,0:14:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴被挾持為人質
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逼迫你做出痛苦的抉擇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.04,0:15:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而同伴的性命也會因此難保
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.91,0:15:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們所執行的任務 都是玩命的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們來看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有無數姓名刻在這石頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些全都是被村民稱為英雄的忍者們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個 就是這個 就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就喜歡這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定也要把名字刻上去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄 英雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼能這麼輕易地掛掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.56,0:15:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這不是普通的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.84,0:15:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼樣的英雄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.25,0:15:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快說嘛 快說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們都是殉職的英雄們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殉職
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是為了執行任務而身亡的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是慰靈碑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.12,0:16:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有好幾個朋友的名字刻在這石碑上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.10,0:16:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再給你們最後一次機會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.74,0:16:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 下午之後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搶鈴鐺的戰鬥會變得更加激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有想挑戰的人才能吃便當
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.31,0:16:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是決不許給鳴人吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是他不守規矩 想吃獨食的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人敢分給他吃的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就淘汰掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.79,0:16:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡 我就是規則
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.21,0:17:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 伊魯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論結果如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.74,0:17:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不要恨卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算沒吃飯 也不會怎麼樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.27,0:17:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我沒有任何影響
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.13,0:17:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才老師不是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.38,0:17:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正他現在也不在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.26,0:17:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午我們三人一起去搶鈴鐺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你礙手礙腳的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.02,0:17:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還傷腦筋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.26,0:18:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.25,0:18:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用謝了 趕快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.90,0:18:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.93,0:18:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在減肥…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.41,0:18:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 因為我吃得比佐助少
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.56,0:18:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你不用放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.69,0:18:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.50,0:18:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.13,0:18:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天曉得他什麼時候出現
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.89,0:18:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎 你應該很清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦 知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:19:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.48,0:19:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的膽子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然敢違抗我訂的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.18,0:19:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還有什麼想說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因…因為
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.15,0:19:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…因為…因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.72,0:19:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 不是你自己說的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.74,0:19:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他們才會…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.51,0:19:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是三人小組對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.04,0:19:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們三個人一條心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 就是啊 就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.32,0:19:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人一條心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:19:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.23,0:20:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合格…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個是第一批
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.87,0:20:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的小鬼們只會乖乖聽我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者要沉著冷靜地判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打破忍者世界的規則和鐵律的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.64,0:20:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都叫他廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.17,0:20:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂得重視同伴的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是更差勁的廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.52,0:20:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是…真是太帥了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演習到此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.35,0:20:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體合格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.25,0:20:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第7班從明天起開始執行任務
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.59,0:20:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 我成為忍者咯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:20:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.01,0:21:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就知道會這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快幫我解開繩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.39,0:22:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.69,0:22:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼都是這種不入流的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.63,0:22:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為有像樣一點的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.25,0:22:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果居然是護送這種老頭子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.15,0:23:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為我們是小鬼就瞧不起我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.26,0:23:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會借此機會好好表現的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.45,0:23:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老頭子 你給我聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.26,0:23:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將來可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.86,0:23:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有在聽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.55,0:23:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.24,0:23:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要任務 向波之國出發
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.06,0:23:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴你 我還會繼續表現的哦
